title: 'Nothing special in Signora ware'
body: 'I have purchased 6.5 litres container. When I tested for leakage I found it leaking from the corners. I returned it to Amazon for the replacement with good one. The replaced container is also leaking. The manufacturer says that their products are spill proof but it is not. If you really want a product which is leak proof then go for Tupperware. Very disappointed with the Signora Ware quality.'
